)

SELECT
    toInt64(
        sum(key * value) / sum(value)
    ) AS avg_duration
FROM (
    SELECT
        arrayJoin(arrayZip(mapKeys(duration_map), mapValues(duration_map))) AS kv_pair,
        kv_pair.1 AS key,
        kv_pair.2 AS value
    FROM
        $table
    WHERE
        $timeFilter
        AND (length('$planId') = 0 OR arrayExists(x -> (x = plan_id), arrayMap(x -> toInt64(x), splitByChar(',', coalesce('$planId', '')))))
        AND (length('$taskId') = 0 OR arrayExists(x -> (x = task_id), arrayMap(x -> toInt64(x), splitByChar(',', coalesce('$taskId', '')))))
)
